<div class="entrycontent">The default chat client in Karmic, the next Ubuntu release, is empathy, and it forces you to save all passwords.<br /><br />Complain here:  <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/empathy/+bug/118800">https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+sour<wbr />ce/empathy/+bug/118800</a><br />(Or let me know if you have a better idea.)<br /><br />Update:  This is now marked high priority for the Karmic release, so I expect it to get fixed.</div>

